@startuml
title DNAT - Sequencia de Startup da VM1

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #2E4057
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam sequence {
  LifeLineBorderColor #486581
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F7FAFC
  ParticipantBorderColor #486581
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontColor #102A43
  ActorBorderColor #486581
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorFontColor #102A43
}

actor "Operador" as User
participant "docker compose\nfrontend-vm.compose.yaml" as Compose
participant "docker build\nDockerfile" as Dockerfile
participant "container dnat-client\nENTRYPOINT=tini" as Container
participant "root-entrypoint.sh" as Entry
participant "IPFS daemon" as IPFS
participant "Hardhat node" as Hardhat
participant "deploy.js" as Deploy
participant "api-server.js" as Api

User -> Compose : docker compose up -d --build
Compose -> Dockerfile : build image da CVM1

activate Dockerfile
Dockerfile -> Dockerfile : copia binario `ipfs`\ninstala pacotes base
Dockerfile -> Dockerfile : npm ci em `smart-contract/`
Dockerfile -> Dockerfile : copia `root-entrypoint.sh`
Dockerfile -> Compose : imagem `dnat-client-local`
deactivate Dockerfile

Compose -> Container : cria container\ninjeta env/ports/volume/rede
activate Container
Container -> Entry : executa via `tini`
activate Entry

Entry -> Entry : resolve defaults de ambiente
Entry -> Entry : cria `/data/ipfs`\ne `/app/smart-contract/executions`

alt repo IPFS ainda nao existe
  Entry -> IPFS : `ipfs init --profile=server`
end

Entry -> IPFS : `ipfs daemon --migrate=true`
activate IPFS
Entry -> IPFS : wait_for_http POST `/api/v0/version`
IPFS --> Entry : API pronta

Entry -> Hardhat : `npx hardhat node --hostname 0.0.0.0`
activate Hardhat
Entry -> Hardhat : wait_for_http POST JSON-RPC `eth_chainId`
Hardhat --> Entry : RPC pronta

Entry -> Deploy : `npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network localhost`
activate Deploy
Deploy --> Entry : contrato implantado
deactivate Deploy

Entry -> Api : `node scripts/api-server.js`
activate Api
Api --> Entry : processo principal em execucao

note right of Entry
Ordem obrigatoria:
1. IPFS
2. Hardhat
3. deploy do contrato
4. API/web
end note

note right of Compose
`frontend-vm.compose.yaml` define:
- build context
- env vars
- portas
- volume IPFS
- rede `dnat-runtime`
end note

deactivate Api
deactivate Entry
deactivate Container

@enduml
